\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \sigma^{i},\sigma^{j}\right\} =2\delta^{ij},\left(\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)^{2}=p^{i}\sigma^{i}p^{j}\sigma^{j}=p^{2}$
\end_inset

