\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于一个费米子链，宇称变换相当于
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{\psi}O(p)\psi\to\bar{\psi}(\tilde{x})\gamma^{0}O(\tilde{p})\gamma^{0}\psi(\tilde{x})
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $O(p)$
\end_inset

是一串伽马矩阵的乘积。对应的旋量的变换是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{u}(p)O(p)u(p)\to\bar{u}(\tilde{p})\gamma^{0}O(\tilde{p})\gamma^{0}u(\tilde{p})
\]

\end_inset

最后一个等号利用了旋量的性质。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
双线性型的变化形式如下，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
P\bar{\psi}(x)\psi(x)P & =+\bar{\psi}\psi(\tilde{x})\\
P\bar{\psi}(x)\gamma^{\mu}\psi(x)P & =\bar{\psi}\gamma^{\mu\dagger}\psi(\tilde{x})\\
P\bar{\psi}(x)i\gamma^{5}\psi(x)P & =-\bar{\psi}i\gamma^{5}\psi(\tilde{x})\\
P\bar{\psi}(x)\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{5}\psi(x)P & =-\bar{\psi}\gamma^{\mu\dagger}\gamma^{5}\psi(\tilde{x})\\
P\bar{\psi}(x)i\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi(x)P & =\bar{\psi}i\sigma^{\mu\nu\dagger}\psi(\tilde{x})
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中的
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

因子是为了保证整个量是厄米(Hermitian)的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
注意，对于正反费米子，宇称变换有一个相对负号。这很重要。对于一个 femion-antifermion state 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{\vec{p}}^{s\dagger}b_{\vec{q}}^{r\dagger}\ket{0}$
\end_inset

，应用
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

变换，会变成
\begin_inset Formula $-\left(a_{\vec{p}}^{s\dagger}b_{\vec{q}}^{r\dagger}\ket{0}\right)$
\end_inset

，会出现一个额外负号。对于束缚态，如果空间波函数在
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{x}\to-\vec{x}$
\end_inset

下，没有负号，那么总的态函数将是 odd parity，也就是会有个负号。如果空间波函数是反对称的，那么总的态函数是 even parity。所以
\begin_inset Formula $J=0$
\end_inset

是赝标量，
\begin_inset Formula $J=1$
\end_inset

是矢量。可以应用到电子偶素和夸克反夸克系统上。（比如低能介子八重态）
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
时间反演
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在时间反演下，所有矢量的时间部分加个负号，
\begin_inset Formula $p^{\mu}\to\tilde{p}^{\mu}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{p}^{\mu}=(p^{0},-\vec{p})$
\end_inset

。也就是动量反向。同理，
\begin_inset Formula $x^{\mu}\to\tilde{x}^{\mu}$
\end_inset

。还要考虑自旋翻转方向。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U(T)a_{\vec{p}}^{\uparrow}U(T)^{\dagger}\to a_{-\vec{p}}^{\downarrow},\quad U(T)b_{\vec{p}}^{\uparrow}U(T)^{\dagger}\to b_{-\vec{p}}^{\downarrow}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
只有时间改变符号是不行的，不能称为Hilbert 空间中的幺正变换:
\series default

\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\psi(t,\vec{x}) & =\exp\left(iHt\right)\psi(\vec{x})\exp\left(-iHt\right)\\
\Rightarrow & U(T)\psi(t,\vec{x})U(T)=\exp\left(iHt\right)T\psi(\vec{x})T\exp\left(-iHt\right)\\
\Rightarrow & U(T)\psi(t,\vec{x})U(T)\ket{0}=\exp\left(iHt\right)T\psi(\vec{x})T\ket{0}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

这里使用了场的平移对称性和真空能量为
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

。左边是正频解求和（
\begin_inset Formula $\approx\exp\left(-iHt\right)\psi(\vec{x})\ket{0}$
\end_inset

），右边是负频解求和(
\begin_inset Formula $\approx\exp\left(iHt\right)\psi(\vec{x})\ket{0}$
\end_inset

)，所以一定不成立。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以必须使用反线性（or 反幺正）定义，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T.(\text{c-number})=(\text{c-number})^{\ast}.T
\]

\end_inset

由于复共轭运算不是线性运算，所以被称为反线性or反幺正算符。
\begin_inset Formula $A^{\ast}$
\end_inset

不能表示成
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的线性组合。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在方向
\begin_inset Formula $\theta,\phi$
\end_inset

的自旋本征矢量为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi(\uparrow)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\cos\frac{\theta}{2}\\
e^{i\phi}\sin\frac{\theta}{2}
\end{array}\right),\quad\xi(\downarrow)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
-e^{-i\phi}\sin\frac{\theta}{2}\\
\cos\frac{\theta}{2}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明，方向
\begin_inset Formula $\theta,\phi$
\end_inset

的矢量为
\begin_inset Formula $(\sin\theta\cos\phi,\sin\theta\sin\phi,\cos\theta)$
\end_inset

，对应的
\begin_inset Formula $SU(2)$
\end_inset

矩阵为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\cos\theta & \sin\theta\cos\phi-i\sin\theta\sin\phi\\
\sin\theta\cos\phi+i\sin\theta\sin\phi & -\cos\theta
\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\cos\theta & \sin\theta\,e^{-i\phi}\\
\sin\theta\,e^{i\phi} & -\cos\theta
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

用mma求解，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(+1)\to\left(\begin{array}{c}
\cos\frac{\theta}{2}\\
e^{i\phi}\sin\frac{\theta}{2}
\end{array}\right),(-1)\to\left(\begin{array}{c}
-e^{-i\phi}\sin\frac{\theta}{2}\\
\cos\frac{\theta}{2}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

和上面形式一样。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们定义
\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{s}=\left(\xi(\uparrow),\xi(\downarrow)\right)$
\end_inset

,for 
\begin_inset Formula $s=1,2$
\end_inset

。并定义
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi^{-s}=-i\sigma^{2}\left(\xi^{s}\right)^{\ast}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & -1\\
1 & 0
\end{array}\right)\left(\xi^{s}\right)^{\ast}
\]

\end_inset

相当于
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(+1)\to\left(\begin{array}{c}
-e^{-i\phi}\sin\frac{\theta}{2}\\
\cos\frac{\theta}{2}
\end{array}\right),(-1)\to\left(\begin{array}{c}
-\cos\frac{\theta}{2}\\
-e^{i\phi}\sin\frac{\theta}{2}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

所以相当于
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi^{-s}=\left(\xi(\downarrow),-\xi(\uparrow)\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{-s}=-i\sigma^{2}\left(\xi^{s}\right)^{\ast}$
\end_inset

这个关系其实可以从更一般的关系推导出来。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sigma^{2}\sigma^{i}\sigma^{2} & =-\sigma^{\ast},i=1,2,3\\
\sigma^{2}\sigma^{\mu}\sigma^{2} & =\tilde{\sigma}{}^{\mu\ast},\mu=0,1,2,3
\end{align*}

\end_inset

所以，如果一个矢量
\begin_inset Formula $\xi$
\end_inset

满足
\begin_inset Formula $(\vec{n}.\vec{\sigma})\xi=+\xi$
\end_inset

，那么
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(\vec{n}\cdot\vec{\sigma})(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{\ast})=-i\sigma^{2}(-\vec{n}\cdot\vec{\sigma})^{\ast}\xi^{\ast}=i\sigma^{2}\xi^{\ast}=-(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{\ast})
\]

\end_inset

注意，根据这个约定，两次反转，会产生一个
\begin_inset Formula $(-1)$
\end_inset

，而不是回到原来的状态。
\begin_inset Formula $-i\sigma^{2}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{s\ast}\right)^{\ast}=-\sigma^{2}\sigma^{2}\xi^{s}=-\xi^{s}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
仿照
\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{-s}=\left(\xi(\downarrow),-\xi(\uparrow)\right)$
\end_inset

，我们定义
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
a_{\vec{p}}^{-s}=\left(a_{\vec{p}}^{2},-a_{\vec{p}}^{1}\right) & \quad b_{\vec{p}}^{-s}=\left(b_{\vec{p}}^{2},-b_{\vec{p}}^{1}\right)\\
\xi^{s}=\left(\xi(\uparrow),\xi(\downarrow)\right) & \quad\xi^{-s}=\left(\xi(\downarrow),-\xi(\uparrow)\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
现在我们把产生湮灭算符和这些旋量联系起来。令
\begin_inset Formula $a_{\vec{p}}^{s}$
\end_inset

湮灭，
\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{s}$
\end_inset

构建的
\begin_inset Formula $u^{s}(p)$
\end_inset

，令
\begin_inset Formula $b_{\vec{p}}^{s}$
\end_inset

湮灭，
\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{-s}$
\end_inset

构建的
\begin_inset Formula $v^{s}(p)$
\end_inset

。这里故意构建的不同，相差一个负号。反正最后场
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

中的
\begin_inset Formula $u^{s}(p),v^{s}(p)$
\end_inset

会被求和掉，所以选取是任意的。只要正交就行。相应地，
\color red

\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U(T)a_{\vec{p}}^{s}U(T)^{\dagger}\to a_{-\vec{p}}^{-s},\quad U(T)b_{\vec{p}}^{s}U(T)^{\dagger}\to b_{-\vec{p}}^{-s}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
利用
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}}\sigma^{2}=\sqrt{\tilde{p}\cdot\sigma}$
\end_inset

，证明：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{p}.\sigma$
\end_inset

的逆矩阵是
\begin_inset Formula $p\cdot\sigma/m^{2}$
\end_inset

。而
\begin_inset Formula $p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}=p^{\ast}\cdot\sigma^{\ast}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $p\cdot\sigma/m^{2}$
\end_inset

可以同时对角化，所以
\begin_inset Formula $p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{p}.\sigma$
\end_inset

可以同时对角化，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}}\sigma^{2}.\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}}\sigma^{2}=\sigma^{2}p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}\sigma^{2}=\tilde{p}.\sigma
\]

\end_inset

所以上面的式子可以直接开方:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}}\sigma^{2}=\sqrt{\tilde{p}\cdot\sigma}
\]

\end_inset

利用这个等式，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u^{-s}(\tilde{p}) & =\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{\tilde{p}\cdot\sigma/m}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{s\ast}\right)\\
\sqrt{\tilde{p}\cdot\bar{\sigma}/m}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{s\ast}\right)
\end{array}\right)=\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
-i\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}/m}\xi^{s\ast}\\
-i\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\bar{\sigma}^{\ast}/m}\xi^{s\ast}
\end{array}\right)\\
 & =-i\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\sigma^{2} & 0\\
0 & \sigma^{2}
\end{array}\right)\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}/m}\xi^{s\ast}\\
\sqrt{p\cdot\bar{\sigma}^{\ast}/m}\xi^{s\ast}
\end{array}\right)\\
 & =-i\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\sigma^{2} & 0\\
0 & \sigma^{2}
\end{array}\right)\left(u^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}\\
{\color{red}u^{-s}(\tilde{p})} & {\color{red}=-\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\left(u^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

设置
\begin_inset Formula $v^{s}(p)$
\end_inset

由
\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{-s}=\left(\xi(\downarrow),-\xi(\uparrow)\right)$
\end_inset

构建，连续两次
\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{-s}=-i\sigma^{2}\left(\xi^{s}\right)^{\ast}$
\end_inset

变换的结果，会出一个负号,
\begin_inset Formula $v^{-s}$
\end_inset

包含
\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{-(-s)}=-\xi^{s}$
\end_inset

：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v^{s}(p)=\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma/m}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{s\ast}\right)\\
-\sqrt{p\cdot\bar{\sigma}/m}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{s\ast}\right)
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
v^{-s}(\tilde{p}) & =\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{\tilde{p}\cdot\sigma/m}\left(-\xi^{s}\right)\\
-\sqrt{\tilde{p}\cdot\bar{\sigma}/m}\left(-\xi^{s}\right)
\end{array}\right)=\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
-i\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}/m}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{s}\right)\\
i\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\bar{\sigma}^{\ast}/m}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{s}\right)
\end{array}\right)\\
 & =-i\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\sigma^{2} & 0\\
0 & \sigma^{2}
\end{array}\right)\left(v^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}\\
u^{-s}(\tilde{p}) & =-\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\left(u^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\color red

\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v^{-s}(\tilde{p})=-\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\left(v^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}
\]

\end_inset


\color inherit
由这些关系，我们得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
T\psi(t,\vec{x})T & =\int\frac{\dif^{3}p}{(2\pi)^{3}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2E_{\vec{p}}}}\sum_{s}a^{-s}(\tilde{p})\left(u^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}\exp\left(ip.x\right)+b^{-s\dagger}(\tilde{p})\left(v^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}\exp\left(-ip.x\right)\\
 & =\left(\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\right)\int\frac{\dif^{3}\tilde{p}}{(2\pi)^{3}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2E_{\tilde{p}}}}\sum_{s}a^{-s}(\tilde{p})u^{-s}(\tilde{p})\exp\left(i\tilde{p}.\tilde{x}\right)+b^{-s\dagger}(\tilde{p})v^{-s}(\tilde{p})\exp\left(-i\tilde{p}.\tilde{x}\right)\\
T\psi(t,\vec{x})T & =\left(\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\right)\psi\left(-t,\vec{x}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

利用了
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{p}\cdot\tilde{x}=-\tilde{p}\cdot(-t,\vec{x})$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
同样的，查看双线性型的变化：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T\bar{\psi}(x)T=\left(T\psi(x)T\right)^{\dagger}\gamma^{0}=\psi^{\dagger}(-t,\vec{x})\left(\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\right)^{\dagger}\gamma^{0}=\bar{\psi}(-t,\vec{x})\left(-\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\right)=\bar{\psi}(-t,\vec{x})\left(\gamma^{3}\gamma^{1}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于一个费米子链，时间反演相当于
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{\psi}O(p)\psi\to\bar{\psi}(-t,\vec{x})\left(\gamma^{3}\gamma^{1}\right)O^{*}\left(\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\right)\psi\left(-t,\vec{x}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

是一串伽马矩阵的乘积。对应的旋量的变换是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{u}(p)O(p)u(p)\to\bar{u}(\tilde{p})\gamma^{3}\gamma^{1}O^{*}(\tilde{p})\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}u(\tilde{p})=\bar{u}(p)\gamma^{0}\gamma^{3}\gamma^{1}O^{*}(\tilde{p})\gamma^{1}\gamma^{3}\gamma^{0}u(p)
\]

\end_inset

最后一个等号利用了旋量的性质。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
双线性型的变化形式如下，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
T\bar{\psi}(x)\psi(x)T & =+\bar{\psi}\psi(x^{\prime})\\
T\bar{\psi}(x)\gamma^{\mu}\psi(x)T & =\bar{\psi}\gamma^{\mu\dagger}\psi(x^{\prime})\\
T\bar{\psi}(x)i\gamma^{5}\psi(x)T & =-\bar{\psi}i\gamma^{5}\psi(x^{\prime})\\
T\bar{\psi}(x)\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{5}\psi(x)T & =-\bar{\psi}\gamma^{\mu\dagger}\gamma^{5}\psi(x^{\prime})\\
T\bar{\psi}(x)i\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi(x)T & =\bar{\psi}i\sigma^{\mu\nu\dagger}\psi(x^{\prime})
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $x^{\prime}=(-t,\vec{x})$
\end_inset

，总之，跟宇称变换的结果相似。对于
\begin_inset Formula $i\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

，不要忘记
\begin_inset Formula $i^{\ast}=-i$
\end_inset

，会多一个负号。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
矢量流
\begin_inset Formula $T\bar{\psi}(x)\gamma^{\mu}\psi(x)T$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $j^{0}$
\end_inset

分量不变，其他分量多一个负号。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
电荷共轭
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
电荷共轭习惯上定义成正反费米子之间的变换，自旋方向不变。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Ca_{\vec{p}}^{s}C=b_{\vec{p}}^{s},\quad Cb_{\vec{p}}^{s}C=a_{\vec{p}}^{s}
\]

\end_inset

我们找出
\begin_inset Formula $u^{s}(p)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $v^{s}(p)$
\end_inset

的关系：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left(v^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast} & =\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma/m}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{*}\right)\\
-\sqrt{p\cdot\bar{\sigma}/m}\left(-i\sigma^{2}\xi^{*}\right)
\end{array}\right)^{\ast}=\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
-i\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\bar{\sigma}^{\ast}/m}\xi^{s*}\\
i\sigma^{2}\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma^{\ast}/m}\xi^{s*}
\end{array}\right)^{\ast}\\
 & =\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & -i\sigma^{2}\\
i\sigma^{2} & 0
\end{array}\right)\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{p\cdot\sigma/m}\xi^{s}\\
\sqrt{p\cdot\bar{\sigma}/m}\xi^{s}
\end{array}\right)=-i\gamma^{2}u^{s}(p)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

也就是说，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u^{s}(p)=-i\gamma^{2}v^{s}(p)^{\ast},\quad v^{s}(p)=-i\gamma^{2}u^{s}(p)^{\ast}
\]

\end_inset

所以，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
C\psi(x)C & =\int\frac{\dif^{3}p}{(2\pi)^{3}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2E_{\vec{p}}}}\sum_{s}\left(-i\gamma^{2}b^{s}(p)v^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}e^{-ipx}-i\gamma^{2}a^{s\dagger}(p)\left(u^{s}(p)\right)^{\ast}\exp\left(+ip.x\right)\\
 & =-i\gamma^{2}\psi^{\ast}(x)=-i\gamma^{2}\left(\psi^{\dagger}\right)^{T}=-i\left(\bar{\psi}\gamma^{0}\gamma^{2}\right)^{T}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中使用了
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{2T}=\gamma^{2}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
同样的，查看双线性型的变化：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C\bar{\psi}(x)C=C\psi(x)^{\dagger}C\gamma^{0}=(-i\gamma^{2}\psi)^{T}\gamma^{0}=(-i\gamma^{0}\gamma^{2}\psi)^{T}
\]

\end_inset

可以看到，电荷共轭相当于正反费米子交换了位置，所以再次转置，交换位置的时候会有一个额外的负号。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于一个费米子链，电荷共轭相当于
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{\psi}O\psi\to(\bar{\psi}\gamma^{2}\gamma^{0}O^{T}\gamma^{0}\gamma^{2}\psi)^{T}=-\bar{\psi}\gamma^{2}\gamma^{0}O^{T}\gamma^{0}\gamma^{2}\psi
\]

\end_inset

这个负号跟费米子反对易有关。
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

是一串伽马矩阵的乘积。对应的旋量的变换是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{u}(p)O(p)u(p)\to-\bar{u}(p)\gamma^{2}\gamma^{0}O^{T}(p)\gamma^{0}\gamma^{2}u(p)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
双线性型的变化形式如下，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
C\bar{\psi}(x)\psi(x)C & =+\bar{\psi}\psi(x)\\
C\bar{\psi}(x)\gamma^{\mu}\psi(x)C & =-\bar{\psi}\gamma^{\mu}\psi(x)\\
C\bar{\psi}(x)i\gamma^{5}\psi(x)C & =+\bar{\psi}i\gamma^{5}\psi(x)\\
C\bar{\psi}(x)\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{5}\psi(x)C & =+\bar{\psi}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{5}\psi(x)\\
C\bar{\psi}(x)i\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi(x)C & =-\bar{\psi}i\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi(x)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
CPT变换总结
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
以下均在Weyl 表象下
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\color red
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

变换下：粒子，系数（旋量和场）的变换，它们是相互协调的：
\color inherit

\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U(P)a_{\vec{p}}^{s}U(p)^{\dagger}\to a_{-\vec{p}}^{s},\quad U(P)b_{\vec{p}}^{s}U(p)^{\dagger}\to-b_{-\vec{p}}^{s}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u(p) & =\gamma^{0}u(\tilde{p})\\
v(p) & =-\gamma^{0}v(\tilde{p})\\
P\psi(x)P & =\gamma^{0}\psi(\tilde{x})\\
P\bar{\psi}(x)P & =\bar{\psi}(\tilde{x})\gamma^{0}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{x}=(t,-\vec{x})$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{0}=\text{\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & 1\\
